{
  "stem": "444.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when we came about-- a few miles from Lublin, he opened the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he was, evidently, a fine Polish fellow that helped me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, at Lublin with my brother, we went to a smaller town, where we thought it would be easier to survive the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was the town of Zamosc.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's where my present life-- wife lived with her family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there I was working for a company called Bauleitung der Luftwaffe, which was a company that built airfields.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was-- I was hired by the chief engineer, and he told me to organize so-and-so many electricians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since I couldn't find, in that town, any electricians to my standard, I got the idea that I'd go to a Jewish-- there was a small Jewish labor camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got the idea, I went up there-- if there are any Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the commander of that camp got them all together and said all the electricians-- is anybody an electrician?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So about 12 guys stepped out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I found out there was only one electrician.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They all had nothing to do with the electrical business, but-- but they wanted out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was able to accommodate them in the school where we had the magazine-- there was a school that was a place where the German craftsman lived, and I managed to get one classroom.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got only 12 guys, I believe, in that classroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was able to get them some-- some blankets, and they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They worked in the-- I had a magazine up there with a lot of electrical equipment, because we were building six airfields around that-- that town of Zamosc.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the Germans, before the war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were preparing for the war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
